movies.title: Hai, Romania!

Go Romania.—Canon y mus

movies.title: Maidaan
movies.summary: Syed Abdul Rahim coach of Indian football team is to be sacked after their big defeat in 1952 Olympics but he defends himself citing major reason of defeat was management failure.Rahim eyes the 1956 Olympics and wants to choose the team himself he gets talent from allover the country but media tycoon Mr Roy and management of football committee aren't happy with him as they favor only Bengal players. At 1956 Olympics the team finishes at fourth position which remains an overall record till date but at 1960 Olympics when the team is out in first round and Rahim is sacked by management thou the team received appreciation from French fans in a match against their team.This becomes a testing time for Rahim personally as well as professionally as he is diagnosed with lung cancer and has short time to live but he dreams of coaching the Indian football team again for 1962 Asian Games.—alex.mjacko@gmail.com

movies.title: Manjummel Boys
movies.summary: A group of ten friends known as Manjummel Boys go for a trip at Kodaikanal and enjoy the adventure.On their return journey one friend suggests the Guna Caves where famous Kamal Hassan movie Guna was shot.The friends reach the cave and enter restricted area even after seeing warning signs they all explore and enjoy the adventure inside the caves.Until one of the friend Subhash falls into a hole whose depth cannot be measured all friends try possible ways to connect with him but nothing works.The friends decide to take help of locals,forest guard and cops but all have one common answer for them that the hole is a devil's kitchen and till date no one has come out alive.—alex.mjacko@gmail.com

movies.title: Billy & Molly: An Otter Love Story
movies.title_english: Billy & Molly: An Otter Love Story
movies.title_long: Billy & Molly: An Otter Love Story (2024)
movies.summary: When a wild otter in desperate need of help washes up on his jetty in the remote Shetland Islands, Billy, his wife Susan, and their devoted sheepdog Jade accept a unique new member into their family. Billy is at a crossroads when he meets the otter he later names Molly: "Sometimes when you get everything you want, you convince yourself it's everything you need. You convince yourself you're happy..." She fills a need in him that he didn't realize he had. So, while Billy is there for Molly, bringing her back from the brink by providing food and shelter, Molly is also there for Billy, waking something deep inside him that had gone dormant. Billy and Molly: An Otter Love Story is a breathtakingly beautiful documentary, brimming with wonder, curiosity and joy, that shows how love can reawaken us to the power of acceptance (of ourselves and others) and the perfection of nature and life itself.—Canon y mus

movies.title: Dune: Part Two
movies.summary: Paul Atreides unites with Chani and the Fremen while on a warpath of revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family. Facing a choice between the love of his life and the fate of the known universe, he endeavors to prevent a terrible future only he can foresee.—Warner Bros. Pictures
